<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Elisabeth von Bayern, Burggräfin von Nürnberg</head><p>Der Rat teilt Unkenntnis über Wildfänger aus Nürnberg und über Wildfänger nach Rebhühnern bei Cadolzburg mit.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_329" id="164r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_329_r2l2">Burggrefin / </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_329_r2l4">Gnedıge fraw / Als vns ewr gnad <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hat wie 
<add><ab facs="#facs_329_r2l3">ew <expan>fürkume<ex>n</ex></expan> ſeÿ / daʒ </ab></add> etliche die <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_329_r2l5">vaſte lawffen vnd wildt vahen ſüllen / . Davon wiſſen wir nichtes </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_329_r2l6">vnd ſo hat vns auch <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> gnad nyemant benant / . Dann weſt ewr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_329_r2l7">gnad yemant der <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> / der <expan>darynne<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>meldet</expan> wer / den 
<add><ab facs="#facs_329_r1l1">
<del rend="strikethrough">d </del> lıeʒʒet vns </ab><ab facs="#facs_329_r1l2"><expan>mitname<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab><ab facs="#facs_329_r1l3">vvıſſen / So </ab></add> <expan>vvolt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir die </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_329_r2l8">darumb 
<del rend="strikethrough">cʒereden ſecʒen </del> <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> beſenden vnd cʒe rede ſecʒen / vnd das 
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>vnt<ex>er</ex></expan></del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_329_r2l9">vvol <expan>vnt<ex>er</ex>ſagen</expan> / . Auch als ewr gnad ſchreıbt <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> hüner wegen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_329_r2l10">weſten wir dheine <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> / die cʒü nahend bey <expan>Kadoltſp<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> gıengen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_329_r2l11">Den <expan>wolt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir das auch <expan>vnt<ex>er</ex>ſagen</expan> / . vnd wo vvir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_329_r2l12">gedienen <expan>möcht<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / Das <expan>tet<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>allcʒ<ex>eit</ex></expan> <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>eria</ex></expan> ıj̃ . <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Egıdıȷ </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_329" id="164r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Burggrefin</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Gnedige fraw, als uns ewr gnad <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schr<ex>iben</ex></expan>
                        hat, wie <add>ew <expan>fürkume<ex>n</ex></expan> sey, daz</add> etliche die
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> vaste lawffen und wildt vahen süllen,
                        davon wissen wir nichtes und so hat uns auch <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
                        gnad nyemant benant. Dann west ewr gnad yemant der
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>, der <expan>darynne<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>meldet</expan> wer, den <add>liezzet uns
                                    <expan>mitname<ex>n</ex></expan> wissen, so</add>
<expan>wolt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir die darumb <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan>
                        besenden und cze rede seczen und das wol <expan>unt<ex>er</ex>sagen</expan>.
                        Auch als ewr gnad schreibt <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> hüner wegen, westen wir dheine
                                <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>, die czü nahend bey
                                <expan>Kadoltsp<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> giengen, den
                                <expan>wolt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir das auch
                            <expan>unt<ex>er</ex>sagen</expan>. Und wo wir
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> gedienen <expan>möcht<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, das
                                <expan>tet<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>allcz<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>eria</ex></expan> ii <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Egidii.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
